                              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                <h2 class="title-heading-left">Configure the NET IPTV application&nbsp;&nbsp;:</h2>
                                <p>Just go to&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;your device’s&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;store , search for the app, download it and install it.</strong></p>
                                <p>After installation, a message on the home screen is displayed asking you to go to the official website of the application, to activate the application.</p>
                                <p>The MAC address, which is the identifier of your device, it will be used to activate the application.</p>
                                <p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="lazyload lazyload-simple alignnone size-full wp-image-16191 et-lazy-loaded" src="../../smart-iptv.shop/rab-content/uploads/2020/11/Screenshot_24.html" sizes="(max-width: 1131px) 100vw, 1131px" srcset="https://smart-iptv.shop/rab-content/uploads/2020/11/Screenshot_24.png 1131w, https://smart-iptv.shop/rab-content/uploads/2020/11/Screenshot_24-600x302.png 600w, https://smart-iptv.shop/rab-content/uploads/2020/11/Screenshot_24-300x151.png 300w, https://smart-iptv.shop/rab-content/uploads/2020/11/Screenshot_24-1024x515.png 1024w, https://smart-iptv.shop/rab-content/uploads/2020/11/Screenshot_24-768x386.png 768w" alt="Screenshot_24" width="1131" height="569"></p>
                                <p>Then go to the application site at the following address:&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.netiptv.eu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.netiptv.eu/</a></p>
                                <p><strong>NB:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>The application is chargeable (about 5 or 6€).&nbsp;You can test it for a week and then you will have to pay to use it.</strong></p>
                                <p><strong>the application website: https://www.netiptv.eu/Payment</strong></p>
